# üìú THE BOOK OF STULATIONS ‚Äî APPENDIX A: .gitattributes
# This file enforces canonical formatting rules across all timelines.
# For where there is inconsistency, there shall be Merge Conflict.
# And Merge Conflict is the path to suffering.
